\section{\emph{Effective} Action For An Accelerated Charge}
Consider a system of finite-size charged particle coupled with its own electromagnetic field subjected to an external potential $V(\vec x)$. The Lagrangian of such a system of a charged particle plus electromagnetic field reads:


where,
\begin{eqnarray}
